# some-Level Summary of Cryptography Used

bcrypt        → Password hashing (one-way, salted)
HS256 (JWT)   → Token signing & verification
Fernet        → Symmetric encryption for sensitive data
OAuth2        → Secure token flow (Step 14)
.env secrets  → Key management best practice